 the intruder with its horn."},{"version":"gold","text":"This powerful POK\u00e9MON thrusts its prized horn under its enemies\u2019 bellies then lifts and throws them."},{"version":"silver","text":"Usually docile, but if disturbed while sipping honey, it chases off the intruder with its horn."},{"version":"crystal","text":"With its Herculean powers, it can easily throw arou\u00ad nd an object that is 100 times its own weight."},{"version":"ruby","text":"HERACROSS charges in a straight line at its foe, slips beneath the foe\u2019s grasp, and then scoops up and hurls the opponent with its mighty horn. This POK\u00e9MON even has enough power to topple a massive tree."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"HERACROSS has sharp claws on its feet. These are planted firmly into the ground or the bark of a tree, giving the POK\u00e9MON a secure and solid footing to forcefully fling away foes with its proud horn."},{"version":"emerald","text":"They gather in forests seeking the sweet sap of trees. It is completely clad in a steel-hard shell. It is proud of its horn, which it uses to fling foes."},{"version":"firered","text":"Usually docile, but if disturbed while sipping honey, it chases off the intruder with its horn."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"This powerful POK\u00e9MON thrusts its prized horn under its enemies\u2019 bellies, then lifts and throws them."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It gathers in forests to search for tree sap, its favorite food. It\u2019s strong enough to hurl foes."},{"version":"pearl","text":"With powerful legs and claws, it generates enough power to hurl foes over great distances."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It loves sweet honey. To keep all the honey to itself, it hurls rivals away with its prized horn."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"This powerful Pok\u00e9mon thrusts its prized horn under its enemies\u2019 bellies, then lifts and throws them."},{"version":"black","text":"It loves sweet honey. To keep all the honey to itself, it hurls rivals away with its prized horn."},{"version":"white","text":"It loves sweet honey. To keep all the honey to itself, it hurls rivals away with its prized horn."},{"version":"black-2","text":"No matter how heavy its opponents, it flings them far away with its prized horn."},{"version":"white-2","text":"No matter how heavy its opponents, it flings them far away with its prized horn."},{"version":"x","text":"This powerful Pok\u00e9mon thrusts its prized horn under its enemies\u2019 bellies, then lifts and throws them."},{"version":"y","text":"With its Herculean powers, it can easily throw around an object that is 100 times its own weight."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Heracross charges in a straight line at its foe, slips beneath the foe\u2019s grasp, and then scoops up and hurls the opponent with its mighty horn. This Pok\u00e9mon even has enough power to topple a massive tree."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Heracross has sharp claws on its feet. These are planted firmly into the ground or the bark of a tree, giving the Pok\u00e9mon a secure and solid footing to forcefully fling away foes with its proud horn."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It\u2019s proud of its thick horn. In Alola, its biggest rival is Vikavolt, which it\u2019s always fighting with."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It roams through forests searching for sweet nectar. Although it boasts fantastic physical strength, it\u2019s not that good at flying."},{"version":"sword","text":"Heracross loves sweet sap and will go looking through forests for it. The Pok\u00e9mon uses its two antennae to pick up scents as it searches."},{"version":"shield","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon takes pride in its strength, which allows it to lift things 100 times heavier than itself with no trouble at all."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon has an unparalleled horn. Heracross itself demonstrates tremendous power\u2014it's capable of throwing several people trained in the traditional arts of war at once."}